	    <summary lang="en">Apple TV 4 Screensavers in Kodi</summary>
	    <description lang="en">This screensaver addon enables the new Apple TV4 aerial screensavers in Kodi</description>
        <news>v1.4.2  (11/08/2017) [CR]
